      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-quality 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, a pinnacle of 50/50 weight distribution and lightweight kinematics. This example features the legendary 13B-REW rotary engine, with the sequential twin-turbocharger system operating in perfect synchronization\u2014providing a seamless transition at 4,500 RPM without boost drop-off. The chassis retains its factory-spec double-wishbone suspension and Torsen limited-slip differential, delivering surgical handling and communicative feedback. Meticulously serviced with documented compression results and a pristine vacuum line assembly, this FD remains in its original, unmodified configuration. An exceptional opportunity for the purist seeking a mechanically flawless icon of the JDM golden era.",
