      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it\u2019s been pampered since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! We're talking a spotless interior, flawless paint, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019ve been looking for a ride that\u2019s been meticulously loved and kept in pristine condition, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look and fall in love!",
