      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E92 M3, a superlative example of the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated V8 era. This specimen is in concours condition, featuring individual throttle bodies and a factory-correct 8,400 RPM redline that remains visceral and precise. The mechanical provenance is documented, including proactive rod bearing replacement with treated shells and a comprehensive service of the dual-VANOS system to ensure optimal valve timing. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, complemented by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) that provides flawless suspension kinematics. Power is managed via a seven-speed M-DCT gearbox and an M Variable Differential Lock, offering exceptional longitudinal and lateral acceleration. The exterior maintains its original factory depth and luster, while the interior shows no bolster deformation or UV degradation. This is a mechanically transparent, museum-quality vehicle for the collector who demands technical perfection.",
